                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I went through the list on allakhazams and pulled out all the focus's that looked to me like they could be used on our spells and would be remotely worthwhile..... (note I did not use the enhanced versions of these focus's because I thought it would be more difficult to sort out the focus's)
<br />

<br />
Affliction Efficiency IV
<br />
1: Decrease Spell Mana Cost by 25%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Spell Type(Detrimental only)
<br />
4: Limit: Min Duration(30.00 sec)
<br />
5: Limit: Effect(Hitpoints allowed)
<br />

<br />
Affliction Haste IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Haste by 33%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Min Duration(30.00 sec)
<br />
4: Limit: Min Casting Time(3.00 sec)
<br />
5: Limit: Spell Type(Detrimental only)
<br />
6: Limit: Effect(Hitpoints allowed)
<br />

<br />
Burning Affliction IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Damage by 20%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Spell Type(Detrimental only)
<br />
4: Limit: Min Duration(30.00 sec)
<br />
5: Limit: Effect(Hitpoints allowed)
<br />

<br />
Enhancement Haste IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Haste by 30%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Min Duration(72.00 sec)
<br />
4: Limit: Min Casting Time(3.00 sec)
<br />
5: Limit: Spell Type(Beneficial only)
<br />

<br />
Extended Enhancement IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Duration by 15%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Spell Type(Beneficial only)
<br />
4: Limit: Effect(Complete Heal (with duration) excluded)
<br />
5: Limit: Effect(Invunerability excluded)
<br />
6: Limit: Min Duration(48.00 sec)
<br />
7: Limit: Effect(Reaction Radius excluded)
<br />

<br />
Extended Range IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Range by 15%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />

<br />
Extended Torment IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Duration by 10%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Min Duration(24.00 sec)
<br />
4: Limit: Effect(Complete Heal (with duration) excluded)
<br />
5: Limit: Effect(Charm excluded)
<br />
6: Limit: Spell Type(Detrimental only)
<br />
7: Limit: Effect(Reaction Radius excluded)
<br />

<br />
Improved Damage IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Damage by 20%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Effect(Hitpoints allowed)
<br />
4: Limit: Instant spells only
<br />
5: Limit: Spell Type(Detrimental only)
<br />
6: Limit: Target(AE PC v1 excluded)
<br />
7: Limit: Target(PB AE excluded)
<br />
8: Limit: Target(Targeted AE excluded)
<br />
9: Limit: Target(Uber Giants excluded)
<br />
10: Limit: Target(Uber Dragons excluded)
<br />

<br />
Innoruuk's Sarcasm
<br />
1: Decrease Spell/Bash Hate by 40%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Effect(Poison Counter allowed)
<br />

<br />
Mana Preservation IV
<br />
1: Decrease Spell Mana Cost by 10%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Spell(Complete Healing excluded)
<br />
4: Limit: Effect(Percentage Heal excluded)
<br />

<br />
Spell Haste IV
<br />
1: Increase Spell Haste by 15%
<br />
2: Limit: Max Level(65)
<br />
3: Limit: Spell(Complete Healing excluded)
<br />
4: Limit: Min Casting Time(3.00 sec)
<br />
5: Limit: Effect(Percentage Heal excluded)
<br />

<br />
anyways.... im trying to decide what I want as some goal items and it has alot to do with what focus effects I want to keep on my character, I just wanted to find some opinions of other enchanters of what focus items they use...</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Aerion Velwin
<br />
