                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">In order of importance....
<br />

<br />
Mana Preservation - best focus for all casters
<br />

<br />
Spell Haste - very effective for charming and slowing, also nice for buffs.
<br />

<br />
Extended Range - very good for charming and most any spell. Great for avoiding AEs during those style of fight.
<br />

<br />
Everything else - Gravy.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />When I was young I used to pray to God that He would give me a new bicycle. I soon found out that God didn't work that way, so I stole a bike and asked Him to forgive me.
