                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I know some of these are Mage only I think but I apologize in advance. Additional "Named Focus" effects, many of which are only on No Drop Items...
<br />

<br />
	Anger of Solusek ~	Increase spell damage 25% on direct damage spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Conservation of Mithaniel ~	Lowers mana cost 15% on buffs level 65 or lower
<br />
	Conservation of Xegony ~	Lowers mana cost 20% on spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Contemplative Alacrity ~	Lowers casting time 15% on spells level 65 or lower and casting time 3 sec or more
<br />
	Conundrum of Speed ~	Lowers casting time 15% on spells level 65 or lower and casting time 3 sec or more
<br />
	Darkened Preservation ~	Lowers mana cost 20% on buffs level 65 or lower
<br />
	Enchantment of Destruction ~	Increase spell damage 20% on direct damage spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Focus of Mithaniel ~	Lowers mana cost 10% on buffs level 65 or lower
<br />
	Focus of the Orb ~	Lowers mana cost 12% on spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Fury of Solusek ~	Increase spell damage 30% on direct damage spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Gallenite's Chaos ~	Increase spell damage 20% on direct damage spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Haste of Druzzil ~	Lowers casting time 18% on spells level 65 or lower and casting time 3 sec or more
<br />
	Haste of Solusek ~	Lowers casting time 15% on spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Naki's Superior Pernicity ~	Lowers casting time 15% on spells level 65 or lower and casting time 3 or more
<br />
	Obsidian Requiem ~	Lowers mana cost 10% on spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Patience of Eternity ~	Increase spell duration upto 20% on Beneficial spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Patience of Time ~	Increase spell duration upto 20% on Beneficial spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Preservation of Mithaniel ~	Lowers mana cost 20% on buffs level 65 or lower
<br />
	Preservation of the Akheva ~	Lowers mana cost 18% on spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Preservation of Xegony ~	Lowers mana cost 15% on spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Quickening of Druzzil	Lowers casting time 23% on spells level 65 or lower and casting time 3 sec or more
<br />
	Sanguine Conservation ~	Lowers mana cost 40% on SELF buffs level 65 or lower
<br />
	Sanguine Enchantment ~	Lowers mana cost 15% on SELF buffs level 65 or lower
<br />
	Secret of Power ~	Increase spell damage 23% on direct damage spells level 65 or lower
<br />
	Zephyr of Brell ~	Increase spell duration upto 20% on Beneficial spells level 65 or lower</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=793464" target="_blank" class="postlink">Satikkine</a>
