                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">#1 Mana pres- if u cast, then get it.
<br />

<br />
Spell haste is good for Hard ldons and charm soloing (spend about 95% of my time doing those 2)  
<br />

<br />
Extended Range is good for soloing.. rarely see it go off on ldons.
<br />

<br />
I have: SH4, ER4. MP4, ID4 and Innoruuks Sarcasm..
<br />

<br />
About the Mana Pres over FT3.. Mana preservation.  the only time FT>MP is during downtime and right after rezzes.  If u get too many mobs and are chain mezzing, MP is definately better, takes 10% (iirc) off each cast.  It adds up fast.
<br />

<br />
just get em all IMO  <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
