                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A lot of it depends on the situation you're in. Most chanters on raids have a very hard time going oom, unless its a CC intense event. In groups, it also depends on what type of group you're in. Still, I probably would rate Spell haste and Mana pres the 2 highest, like mentioned above. Another must-have for the raiding chanter is either Broken lever or Staff of swiftness for Innoruuk's Sarcasm. While its easily possible to do without either, the benefit of being able to cast tash pretty much right off any fight without getting aggro is huge on raids. Extended range is also very good for several reasons.
<br />

<br />
All in all, i'd attempt to plan ahead on your upgrades to include all the focus effects you want.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=405101" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~daerius1/daeriussig.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
